```r
allDf %>%
  filter(index %in% sinspu) %>%
  filter(rel_ab > 1) %>%
  count(genus) %>%
  arrange(desc(n)) %>%
  slice_max(n,
            n = 10) %>%
  .$genus -> most_prev

allDf %>%
  filter(index %in% sinspu) %>%
  filter(genus %in% most_prev) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = index,
             y = genus,
             fill = rel_ab)) +
  geom_tile() +
  scale_fill_viridis_c() +
  facet_grid(cols = vars(virus.bin),
             scales = \free\"
